import React from 'react';
import { Form, FormField, Button, TextInput, Box } from 'grommet';

function InputFormb() {

  return(
    <>
    <Box justify="center">
    <Box direction="row" alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'small' }} pad="medium"> 
      <Form key={1}>
        <FormField label="Shipment Received By" width="large">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter Shipment Received By" />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Received Date">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter Received Date" />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Delivery Challan No.">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter Delivery Challan No." />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Delivery Challan Date">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter Delivery Challan Date" />
        </FormField>
        <Button key={1} type="submit" alignSelf="center" primary label="Submit"  />
      </Form>
    </Box>
    </Box>
   </> 
  );
}


export default InputFormb;
